        "markdown": "# Script Node Smoke Test\n\n1. Select the **Script Runner** node.\n2. Click **RUN** on the node UI.\n3. Confirm the script updates both target nodes below.\n4. `Output Sink` and `Renderable Target` should change immediately.\n5. Confirm the `result` edge still emits the run payload."
